    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Fine-grain rock largely composed of or derived by erosion of sedimentary silt and clay or any type of rock that contained clay.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
